data.description: SHORT SALE, contingent upon 3rd party approval. HO HO HO, did you ask Santa for a new home! This beautiful home is waiting for you, so reserve that u-haul today! Homeowners have loved this floor plan & neighborhood. You enter the home into a formal living room w/vaulted ceilings. Kitchen has canned lighting, stainless steel farm sink & Bonus alert, they are leaving the fridge. Family room is spacious with sliding doors (dog door) to go to the back yard. Upstairs you will find the bedrooms & baths. Master is spacious with walk in closet, ceiling fan, master bath with adult vanity. Basement is plumbed for bathroom & would be super easy to finish. Yard is fully fenced w/2 gates, massive RV parking, sprinkler system, AC & patio area. 8X15 shed w/barn doors & built in shelves & ready for electric to be installed. Another Bonus alert, they are leaving the hot tub! 3 car garage w/windows, exit door, extra lighting & openers. Has a gas line if you wanted to put in a heater/cooler. No steps going from the garage into the home. This home has so much to offer! Call now for your private showing, you won't be disappointed!
